FBIS4-8422 "dreeu071_a_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 ALBANIA Government Orders Greek Consul To Leave Government Orders Greek Consul To Leave AU1204155294 Tirana Radio Tirana Network in Albanian 1430 GMT 12 Apr 94 AU1204155294 Tirana Radio Tirana Network Albanian BFN [Text] The Albanian Government at noon today declared Khristos Iakovou, Greek general consul in Gjirokaster, persona non grata. The decision was officially stated in a note to Greek Ambassador in Tirana Tsalikis. The note from the Albanian Foreign Ministry states that the decision to expel the Greek consul was based on activities not in accordance with his duties in our country. He is obliged to leave the Republic of Albania within 48 hours from the time of the official note's delivery.
